{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/pacaran-dengan-idol-dan-cosplayer-terkenal-lewat-love-convention/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Pacaran dengan Idol dan Cosplayer Terkenal Lewat Love Convention","content":"\n<p>Pernah <em>nggak</em> <em>sih</em> kalian membayangkan punya pacar orang yang terkenal? Gimana ya rasanya <em>pedekate</em> dengan sosok idol dan mengetahui rahasia pribadinya? Para jomblo merapat! Karena dengan Love Convention, semua bisa! </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55818\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pacaran-dengan-idol-dan-cosplayer-terkenal-lewat-love-convention/attachment/1-327/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Love Convention &#8211; Karakter\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: RAIT Games&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1.jpg\" alt=\"Love Convention - Karakter\" class=\"wp-image-55818\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: RAIT Games</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Love Convention, sebuah <em>game</em> buatan studio <em>game</em> dan ilustrasi lokal bergenre <em>visual novel</em> dan <em>dating simulation</em>. Game yang dapat dimainkan di <em>platform</em> android ini mengambil budaya pop Jepang dan eventnya sebagai setting utamanya.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam Love Convention, pemain bisa bertemu dan mendekati salah satu dari 5 <em>cewek</em> di dalam <em>game.</em> Dalam perjalanan player untuk menjadi lebih dekat dengan salah satu dari <em>cewek</em> ini nanti, player akan dihadapkan dengan berbagai pilihan yang akan mempengaruhi cerita dan akhir dari permainan ini.&nbsp; </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55819\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pacaran-dengan-idol-dan-cosplayer-terkenal-lewat-love-convention/attachment/2-261/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Love Convention &#8211; Momo\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sang Cosplayer, Momo. (Sumber: RAIT Games)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2.jpg\" alt=\"Love Convention - Momo\" class=\"wp-image-55819\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sang Cosplayer, Momo. (Sumber: RAIT Games)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak kurang dari 13 akhir cerita (<em>ending</em>) yang ada dan dapat ditemukan dalam game buatan RAIT game ini. Akankah kisahnya berakhir bahagia atau malah romansa tidak berjalan sesuai rencana tergantung dari bagaimana pemain menentukan pilihannya selama permainan.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55820\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pacaran-dengan-idol-dan-cosplayer-terkenal-lewat-love-convention/attachment/3-284/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Love Convention &#8211; Enako\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Maid, Enako. (Sumber: RAIT Games)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/3.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/3.jpg\" alt=\"Love Convention - Enako\" class=\"wp-image-55820\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Maid, Enako. (Sumber: RAIT Games)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Cewek-cewek yang dapat ditemui di game ini antara lain Momo sang <em>cosplayer,</em> Dona si <em>cewek</em> penyuka game, Yuko sang artis ternama, guru sekaligus komikus bernama Tania, dan Enako sang maid. Kalau diperhatikan, masing-masing cewek bakal mewakili satu sub budaya dari budaya populer Jepang. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Game yang sudah bisa diunduh di Google Playstore ini memiliki cerita yang dalam mengenai permasalahan-permasalahan yang terjadi seputar dunia budaya popular Jepang di Indonesia.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55824\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pacaran-dengan-idol-dan-cosplayer-terkenal-lewat-love-convention/attachment/7-169/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Love Convention &#8211; Jalan Cerita\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: RAIT games&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/7.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/7.jpg\" alt=\"Love Convention - Jalan Cerita\" class=\"wp-image-55824\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: RAIT games</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Game ini bermula dari ide random yang keluar dari curhatan salah satu anggota tentang kesulitan mendapatan pacar. Dari pertanyaan “gimana ya rasanya pacaran sama x (nama <em>cosplayer</em> terkenal di Indonesia)?” </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Akhirnya tim RAIT game memutuskan untuk memulai <em>project</em> Love Convention. Project ini sendiri telah memiliki serial webtoon yang telah terbit satu season sebanyak 24 episode.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55825\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pacaran-dengan-idol-dan-cosplayer-terkenal-lewat-love-convention/attachment/8-137/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Love Convention &#8211; Game\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: RAIT Games&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/8.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/8.jpg\" alt=\"Love Convention - Game\" class=\"wp-image-55825\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: RAIT Games</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>RAIT game adalah divisi pengembangan game dari studio ilustrasi <a href=\"http://raitvisualworks.com/\">RAIT Visual Works</a>. Bekerja sama dengan <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Japan.Culture.Daisuki/\">Japan Culture Daisuki</a>, media dan <em>event organizer</em> acara bertemakan budaya populer Jepang, mereka ingin memberikan hiburan dan pengalaman tentang dunia budaya populer Jepang. Game ini sudah dirilis di <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.RAIT.Loveconbeta&amp;hl=es_NI\">Playstore</a> dan baru tersedia untuk platform Android. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalian bisa mengunjungi laman Love Convention di <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/loveconvention/\">Instagram</a>, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/loveconventions/\">Facebook </a>dan halaman <a href=\"https://www.webtoons.com/id/challenge/love-convention/list?title_no=275228\">Webtoon</a> mereka.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"1a2704a0-6834-5faf-9b9f-f6a4466ceb56"}}}